goodnight , vienna ( also known as magic night ) is a 1932 british musical film directed by herbert wilcox and starring jack buchanan , anna neagle and gina malo . two lovers in vienna are separated by the first world war , but are later reunited . it was based on a radio operetta written by eric &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; . it features the song " &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , vienna " . wilcox reportedly cast neagle , whom he would later marry and direct in many films , after discovering her by chance in a stage show .